        "id": 1006192
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-03-15T00:50:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There is no need to return a map here.\nWe want to just return a list of files owned by the owner and not banned from auto-approval.\n\nIf any of the files is banned, we just return nothing (either an `Optional\u003cMap\u003c\u003e\u003e` or simply a `null`), indicating that the processing should stop.\n\n\n\n```suggestion\n  @Nullable\n  public Set\u003cString\u003e filterFilesOwnedByWithAutoOwnersApproved(\n```",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 95,
        "startChar": 9,
        "endLine": 95,
        "endChar": 40
      },
      "revId": "30419d13cf80bda06ddbc5f66913290fb7aa1675",
      "serverId": "173816e5-2b9a-37c3-8a2e-48639d4f1153"
    },
