      "message": "Short-circuiting can no longer be used because even if the any of the files is banned, we still want to return the _complete set of owned files_ since we have to fall back to the default logic.\n\nI have updated this method to return a `record` that encapsulate both the list of filtered owned files and a boolean indicating whether the owner owns at least one file that is banned from auto owners approval.",
